"Senior Azure Cloud Architect with Java EE and Spring Boot experience"

JOB OVERVIEW

Plan A Technologies is looking for a Senior Azure Cloud Architect with Java EE and Spring Boot experience to join our team. The job involves defining the architecture for several applications and supporting software engineering during development.

Please note: you must have at least seven years of experience in software development and/or architecture to be considered for this job.

JOB RESPONSIBILITY

Assess business requirements and conduct gap assessments between on-the-shelf products and requirements.

Understand and shape functional and non-functional requirements.

Outline roadmap for product & solutions.

Propose specific high-level designs.

Support estimation.

Document architecture.

Support implementation team with guidance during implementation.

Participate in developing designed architectures.

Support troubleshooting when required.

EXPERIENCE

Experience in software development and/or architecture (7+ years strongly preferred, 10+ years a plus).

Expert in Microsoft Azure: must be an expert in cloud services provisioning, design, and implementation.

Experience with Azure Kubernetes Service

At least 2 years of experience with Java EE and Spring Boot

Experience with OOD & OOP is a plus.

Experience with databases.

Experience with AKS, Springboot, Java EE

Experience with building web technologies.

Experience with handling application design.

Experience with CICD, Containers.

Basic knowledge of modeling (like UML).

General knowledge about IT and the IT industry.

Excellent written and verbal English skills.

ABOUT THE COMPANY/BENEFITS

Plan A Technologies is an American software development and technology advisory firm that brings top-tier engineering talent to clients around the world. Our software engineers tackle custom product development projects, staff augmentation, major integrations and upgrades, and more. The team is far more hands-on than the giant outsourcing shops but still big enough to handle significant enterprise clients.

Read more about us here: www.PlanAtechnologies.com

Location: Work From Home 100% of the time, or come into one of our global offices. Up to you.

Great colleagues and an upbeat work environment: You'll join an excellent team of support engineers and project managers who work hard but never compete with each other.

Benefits: Vacation, Brand New Laptop, and More: You’ll get a generous vacation schedule and other goodies.

If this sounds like you, we'd love to hear from you!
